quran[17]{c,v,t}:
  26,53,Fir‘aon sì rán àwọn akónijọ sínú àwọn ìlú (láti sọ pé)
  26,54,"Dájúdájú àwọn (ọmọ ’Isrọ̄’īl) wọ̀nyí, ìjọ péréte díẹ̀ ni wọ́n"
  26,55,Àti pé dájúdájú wọ́n ti ṣe ohun t’ó ń bí wa nínú
  26,56,Dájúdájú gbogbo wa ni kí á sì wà tìfura-tìfura
  26,57,"Nítorí náà, A mú (ìjọ Fir‘aon) jáde kúrò nínú àwọn ọgbà oko àti ìṣẹ́lẹ̀rú omi"
  26,58,àti àwọn àpótí-ọrọ̀ àti ibùjókòó àpọ́nlé
  26,59,Báyẹn (lọ̀rọ̀ rí). A sì jogún rẹ̀ fún àwọn ọmọ ’Isrọ̄’īl
  26,60,Wọ́n sì lépa wọn ní àsìkò tí òòrùn yọ
  26,61,"Nígbà tí ìjọ méjèèjì ríra wọn, àwọn ìjọ (Ànábì) Mūsā sọ pé: “Dájúdájú wọn yóò lé wa bá.”"
  26,62,"(Ànábì) Mūsā sọ pé: “Rárá, dájúdájú Olúwa mi ń bẹ pẹ̀lú mi. Ó sì máa fi ọ̀nà mọ̀ mí.”"
  26,63,"A sì fi ìmísí ránṣẹ́ sí (Ànábì) Mūsā pé: “Fi ọ̀pá rẹ na agbami òkun.” (Ó fi nà á). Ó sì pín (sí ọ̀nà méjìlá). Ìpín kọ̀ọ̀kan sì dà bí àpáta ńlá"
  26,64,"A sì mú ìjọ kejì (ìyẹn, ìjọ Fir‘aon) súnmọ́ ibẹ̀ yẹn"
  26,65,A gba (Ànábì) Mūsā àti gbogbo àwọn t’ó ń bẹ pẹ̀lú rẹ̀ là pátápátá
  26,66,"Lẹ́yìn náà, A tẹ ìjọ kejì rì (sínú agbami)"
  26,67,Dájúdájú àmì wà nínú ìyẹn. Síbẹ̀síbẹ̀ ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn kò jẹ́ onígbàgbọ́ òdodo
  26,68,"Dájúdájú Olúwa rẹ, Òun mà ni Alágbára, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run"
  26,69,Ka ìròyìn (Ànábì) ’Ibrọ̄hīm fún wọn